{"tid":757863,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"係美孚整過mac機嘅入一入黎（長文慎入）","createTime":"2018-07-27T07:36:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T11:28:32.000Z","uid":83798,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4ae18712252965689d0fddef6d9e6527b333a83d","tid":757863,"uid":83798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T07:36:45.000Z","msg":"頭先on99電腦post開錯係吹水台<br />\n我個fd係美孚整mac機mon 好快就打柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人試過咁樣？又唔係平㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以上黎分享下佢個遭遇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我fd:<br />\n真係好後悔無買到AppleCare<br />\n當買個教訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話說我就今年3月22日係Facebook搵左一間口碑唔錯（有成2萬個人讚好㗎）嘅維修Mac機店換mon <br />\n結果7月初 個mon就岀現掉落嘅情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/150520_6be5ba2ed6f11113e73a33e810a604b3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F150520_6be5ba2ed6f11113e73a33e810a604b3.png&h=3c40c1d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再過多廿幾日 即係琴日7月26日 個mon出現咗啲奇怪影子...初頭仲以為係貼紙啲野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/150951_7441bca219dd60c205f7e6f2229809bb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F150951_7441bca219dd60c205f7e6f2229809bb.png&h=52edbb78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日係Facebook 同店主討論，希望可以跟進下，結果俾人block埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好灰...3千蚊整電腦用左三個多月就岀事真係喊岀黎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好後悔無買AppleCare<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.discuss.com.hk/index.php?action=thread&amp;tid=27605277\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.discuss.com.hk%2Findex.php%3Faction%3Dthread%26tid%3D27605277&d=rHN6vsleqB0umXlyQsQjUhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=ceeabee3\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.discuss.com.hk/index.php?action=thread&amp;tid=27605277</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申我的朋友不是我<br />\n又冇得踩上門問間野，因為我個朋友唔係香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16ff29707df5950afba624bfb59805ae35c60031","tid":757863,"uid":97439,"like":18,"dislike":4,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"4ae18712252965689d0fddef6d9e6527b333a83d","tid":757863,"uid":83798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T07:36:45.000Z","msg":"頭先on99電腦post開錯係吹水台<br />\n我個fd係美孚整mac機mon 好快就打柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人試過咁樣？又唔係平㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以上黎分享下佢個遭遇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我fd:<br />\n真係好後悔無買到AppleCare<br />\n當買個教訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話說我就今年3月22日係Facebook搵左一間口碑唔錯（有成2萬個人讚好㗎）嘅維修Mac機店換mon <br />\n結果7月初 個mon就岀現掉落嘅情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/150520_6be5ba2ed6f11113e73a33e810a604b3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F150520_6be5ba2ed6f11113e73a33e810a604b3.png&h=3c40c1d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再過多廿幾日 即係琴日7月26日 個mon出現咗啲奇怪影子...初頭仲以為係貼紙啲野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/150951_7441bca219dd60c205f7e6f2229809bb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F150951_7441bca219dd60c205f7e6f2229809bb.png&h=52edbb78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日係Facebook 同店主討論，希望可以跟進下，結果俾人block埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好灰...3千蚊整電腦用左三個多月就岀事真係喊岀黎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好後悔無買AppleCare<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.discuss.com.hk/index.php?action=thread&amp;tid=2760